  "texts": [
    "\"Current issues arise with the elements of your social media networking app.",
    "Write an ideas and suggestion memo to your manager on the subject of the app, its interface, and how to maintain it.",
    "As a colleague, include recommendations for user-friendliness, logo redesign, and helpful features.",
    "Be sure to define the problem and follow memo writing format.\"",
    "Memo To: [Manager's Name] From: [Your Name] Date: [Today's Date] Subject: Suggestions for Team's Social Media Networking App I am writing to provide suggestions for our team's social media networking app."
